rxvt-beta (2.7.10-4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix assertion error. Closes: #188276.
  * Add a manpage note regarding the lack of scrollbar style support
    in the minimalist rxvt-xterm binary. Closes: #135733.
  * Update the commands for the clean target.
  * Drop handmade postrm - debhelper is better at the job.
  * Add rxvt-ml to the list of conflicting packages because the used
    alternatives in both packages interfere (this package distributes
    rxvt.1.gz which rxvt and rxvt-ml use as an alternative).

